answers.answer: I have been having severe headaches too since I been pregnant I'm 21 weeks...Doctor told me the same things take Tylenol,  drink plenty of fluid and relax. ..that all you can do..getting plenty of relax help me alot.
You may want to go to the ER abd have your blood pressure checked, it can be an early sign of preeclampsia possibly. I know it comes later in pregnancy but you never know.
Try a cool cloth on the back of your neck.
